<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَالْمَرْدُودُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِمَّا إَنْ يَكُونَ رَدُّهُ لِسَقْطٍ مِنَ السَّنَدِ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ طَعْنٍ فِي رَاوٍ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَمَا سَقَطَ أَوَّلُ سَنَدِهِ، تَصَرُّفًا مِنْ مُصَنِّفٍ؛ فَهُوَ الْمُعَلَّقُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَمَا سَقَطَ صَحَابِيُّهُ؛ فَهُوَ الْمُرْسِلُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمَا سَقَطَ مِنْهُ اثْنَانِ فَأَكْثَرُ مَعَ التَّوَاليِ؛ فَهُوَ الْمُعْضَلُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَمَا سَقَطَ مِنْهُ وَاحِدٌ، وَلَوْ فِي مَوَاضِعَ؛ فَهُوَ الْمُنْقَطِعُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَإِنْ خَفِيَ السُّقُوطُ بِأَنَ رَوَى عَنْ مُعَاصِرِهِ شَيئًا لَمْ يَسْمَعْهُ مِنْهُ، بِصِيَغةٍ تَحْتَمِلُ السَّمَاعَ، وَقَدْ عُرِفَ أَنَّهُ لَقِيَهُ؛<span class="c5"> فَهُوَ الْمُدَلَّسُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَإِلَّا:</span> فَهُوَ الْمُرْسَلُ الْخَفِيُّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَالطَّعْنُ يَكُونُ بِوَاحِدٍ مِنْ عَشَرَةِ أَشْيَاءَ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>خَمْسَةٌ تَتَعَلَّقُ بِالْعَدَالَةِ؛<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١ - الكَذِبُ فيِ الْحَدِيثِ النَّبوِيِّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢ - وَالتُّهَمَةُ بِذَلِكَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣ - وَظُهُورُ الْفِسْقِ،.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٤ - وَالْجَهْلُ بِحَالِ الرَّاوِي.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٥ - وَبِدْعَتُهُ المُكَفِّرَةُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَخَمْسَةٌ تَتَعَلَّقُ بِالضَّبْطِ؛<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>١ - فُحْشُ غَلَطِهِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٢ - وَكَثْرَةُ غَفْلَتِهِ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>